{
  "texts": [
    "And sometimes it's okay to stand out differently and not do those things.",
    "This professor clarifies that they are not \"one of those people stuck in their ways\"-they are not against AI adoption altogether.",
    "Instead, they argue that there are people like themselves who \"understand this technology, which is why I don't want to just free fall and go for it.",
    "I want to be more conscientious about it.",
    "I want to really think about these things.\""
  ]
}